This release adds some polish to the meteobrowser by allowing it to
completely localized (however, while it works on Linux, it gettext
seems not to work on Solaris 8.

Furthermore, the meteoloop program has been enhanced to handle some
communication failures more gracefully. The large gaps visible during
january in the example station browsers on http://meteo.othello.ch
should now be a thing of the past


